        <thoughtStageDescriptions>
          <li>Less than {DAYSSINCELASTSPOKENTHRESHOLD} days since our last traditional gathering</li>
          <li>More than {DAYSSINCELASTSPOKENTHRESHOLD} days since our last traditional gathering</li>
        </thoughtStageDescriptions>
      </li>
